data.description: Beautiful large pool home with 1,624sqft under AC. 1444sqft under trusses. One of the largest corner lots on the block. Very well maintained. Pool & lawn serviced weekly. Pool pump replaced March 2023. Pest control serviced monthly. New 2022 roof. Beautiful pool resurfaced in 2022. Entire home painted inside and out 2022. Pool porch new & re-screened 2022. Mandarin, peach & coconut tree. Stainless steel appliances. Being sold AS IS fully furnished but negotiable. Wonderful family home! Centrally located walking distance to 3 shopping centers, Wal-Mart, Hospital, Restaurants, Hardware stores, Grocery stores. Beautiful family neighborhood. Not many homes with pools in Lehigh Acres. Come see it today!
